                <h1>Avendor</h1>
                <p>Avendor is the capital of the Ashir Empire.</p>
                <h2 id="2">History</h2>
                <hr class="solid">
                <p>Avendor is the capital city of the Ashir Empire, located in the heart of the Ashir Valley, which is
                    known for its fertile land and scenic beauty. The city is situated in a valley surrounded by high
                    mountains and is a hub of technological innovation and religious importance.
                    Founded in the year 212 by the legendary warrior and religious figure, Kael Ashir, Avendor was
                    originally a small village that grew into a bustling city as the Ashir Empire expanded. Over the
                    centuries, Avendor became a melting pot of various cultures and traditions, with people from all
                    corners of the empire coming to live and work in the city.
                    The city is known as a hub of commerce, religious pilgrimmage, education, politics and arts. Much of
                    its success has been attributed to the incredible technological advancement that are the imperial
                    gates, teleporters connected to capital cities of other countries.</p>
                <h2 id="3">Population</h2>
