                <h2 id="4">Local Government</h2>
                <hr class="solid">
                <p>In terms of governance, Avendor is ruled by the Emperor of the Ashir Empire, who resides in the
                    Imperial Palace located in the heart of the city. The palace is a sprawling complex of buildings and
                    gardens, and is considered to be one of the most magnificent structures in the world.</p>
                <h2 id="5">Architecture</h2>
                <hr class="solid">
                <p>No info yet :3</p>
                <h2 id="6">Economy</h2>
                <hr class="solid">
                <p>Apart from its religious significance, Avendor is also a center of technological progress. The city
                    is home to several universities and research institutions, where scholars and scientists work to
                    push the boundaries of knowledge in fields such as alchemy, engineering, and medicine. The Ashir
                    Empire is known for its advanced technologies, and Avendor is where many of these groundbreaking
                    inventions are developed.</p>
                <h2 id="7">Culture</h2>
